{"tid":1634313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動建議] 十八區開花 --- 全民撳錢運動","createTime":"2019-10-07T07:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T15:34:53.000Z","uid":18001,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f57a8224ddf76d7bba13c4974107e7f828c4df4b","tid":1634313,"uid":18001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:22:53.000Z","msg":"號召各位聽日十八區去各大銀行排隊撳錢<br />\n時間: 直至銀行營業時間結束為止<br />\n地點: 所有銀行分行 *強烈建議集中總行 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府澄清「以緊急法停市凍資產」屬謠言</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n你相信政府嗎? 林鄭當初聲稱會以對話止暴制亂 最後下場係以實彈血腥鎮壓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府企圖透過澄清謠言平息恐慌, 但共產黨既特色就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">講一套做一套</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想保護自己既資產就必須先下手為強 將資產轉成現金 避免成為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">中共回血劍</span></strong></span>下的刀下亡魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fnm8cHW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFnm8cHW.png&h=4160f563&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府企圖平息恐慌既謊言<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你仲信唔信政府?</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加映<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中文版本&mdash;公眾試閱版&mdash;正文<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1N1rzVWFW0EnJugLGNkYu7A-9-KigPWn4fVEGVDve79k/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1N1rzVWFW0EnJugLGNkYu7A-9-KigPWn4fVEGVDve79k%2Fedit&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn%2FzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=40b06b59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1N1rzVWFW0EnJugLGNkYu7A-9-KigPWn4fVEGVDve79k/edit</a><br />\n警隊涉嫌濫權資料（六／七月）<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1RMY12ApIxNTaOudzjvYXzq6Vc0iE99zJJ2M8t0uOKYI/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1RMY12ApIxNTaOudzjvYXzq6Vc0iE99zJJ2M8t0uOKYI%2Fedit&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn%2FzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=1ff1c4ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1RMY12ApIxNTaOudzjvYXzq6Vc0iE99zJJ2M8t0uOKYI/edit</a><br />\n警隊涉嫌濫權資料（至八月十日）<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1TKPNvv_YqRKF8Y2wRi28J89-VTMIsfNAiFsuXX4g1r8/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1TKPNvv_YqRKF8Y2wRi28J89-VTMIsfNAiFsuXX4g1r8%2Fedit&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn%2FzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=09ed1d9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1TKPNvv_YqRKF8Y2wRi28J89-VTMIsfNAiFsuXX4g1r8/edit</a>"},{"pid":"ba163dc8a3dc929c761da133a951b4d0044d843f","tid":1634313,"uid":18001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:45:27.000Z","msg":"行動post冇人理"},{"pid":"18a94f4562765905616b2fa252a2aa0ef0733807","tid":1634313,"uid":213781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:46:13.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n已經撳緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fada7880e67664570249fe5328a3aa1a078c65a","tid":1634313,"uid":42304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:46:27.000Z","msg":"今日都冇錢襟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"953e270c97cd20c5b4c8e35605a7db8c885237ca","tid":1634313,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:47:57.000Z","msg":"全民㩒爆atm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f3f12db8b6612753a76a6615fec03ed7f167a6","tid":1634313,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JG49P0v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJG49P0v.jpg&h=bfdca82e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">目標一、哂馬</span></strong></span><br />\n由於警狗唔再批不反，即使批左亦會製造衝突。<br />\n為左令和理非可以舒舒服服地出返黎，展示人數同民意，<br />\n所以就利用黃店門外既人龍，製造畫面同話題吸引媒體注意。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">目標二、支持黃色經濟</span></span></strong><br />\n依幾個月生意難免受影響，加上可能被藍絲杯葛，<br />\n良心黃店係好需要大家支持。<br />\n最實際既支持當然就係拎銀包出黎，入錢入錢入錢！<br />\n另外參考連登既食評，由於良心經營既關係，黃店食物質素一般都偏高，<br />\n絕對係win win雙贏！<br />\n<br />\n------------國際文宣------------<br />\n請將買返黎既貨物/食物/單據同排隊盛況<br />\n一齊用<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#Buy4HK</span></span></strong><br />\n放上IG, Twitter, reddit"},{"pid":"3ce142cd0d7afd116d40a6ec7cd9c7c45d4f7adc","tid":1634313,"uid":18001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:05:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa39fd0b718a8d4223a27b16b335722040bf15d","tid":1634313,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:18:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87686c56a97c0b9f56c41df8805f